&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Cusco?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-cusco" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-cusco" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The moment you step into &lt;a href="https://daytrips.techpawz.com/posts/cusco-day-trips/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Cusco&lt;/a&gt;, the air is filled with the scent of fresh bread and the faint aroma of roasting coffee, mingling with the crisp mountain breeze. This city, once the heart of the Inca Empire, is a remarkable blend of ancient history and modern vibrancy. Cobblestone streets wind through neighborhoods where colonial architecture stands proudly alongside Inca ruins, creating a unique atmosphere that draws travelers from all over the world. Cusco is not just a stopover on the way to Machu Picchu; it is a destination that offers a deep dive into &lt;a href="https://daytrips.techpawz.com/posts/cusco-day-trips/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Peru&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rsquo;s history, culture, and natural beauty.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Is Lima Worth Visiting? An Honest Travel Guide with Budget Tips</title><link>https://esim.techpawz.com/posts/lima-peru/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 07:30:53 +0700</pubDate><guid>https://esim.techpawz.com/posts/lima-peru/</guid><description>&lt;script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8772455780561463"
